songs.title: Stars Come Out
songs.lyrics:
[Pre-Chorus]
You light me up
You bring the crowd
I think about this
Every time the stars come out

[Chorus]
You light me up
You chase the clouds
I think about this
Every time the stars come out[x5]
Every time the stars come

[Pre-Chorus]

[Chorus]

[Outro]
You light me up
Every time the stars come
You bring the crowd
Every time the stars come
You light me up
Every time the stars come
You chase the clouds
Every time the stars come
Every time the stars come out[x4]
